name: PWSbUV
description: Proxy Web Serach Engine B made with Ultraviolet (by titaniumnetwork-dev), Ultraviolet is a highly advanced web proxy used for evading internet censorship or accessing websites in a controlled sandbox. It is designed with security and performance in mind. Ultraviolet intercepts HTTP requests with a service worker, while adhering to the TompHTTP specifications and is a leader in innovative web proxy technologies.
